NAME
    cosmic - a fail-safe network RAID

SYNOPSIS
      # connect to and create a new fs
      cosmic connect --create device-info /dev/md0
      fdisk -t ext3 /dev/md0
      mount /dev/md0 /var/md0
  
      # connect to and mount an existing volume
      cosmic connect device-info /dev/md0
      mount /dev/md0 /var/md0
  
      # unmount and disconnect volume
      umount /var/md0
      cosmic disconnect device-info /dev/md0

DESCRIPTION
    Cosmic is a fail-safe network RAID, built around iSCSI.

